money on the children.

01:00:14.720 --> 01:00:16.650
And as you have fewer children,
you're spending less

01:00:16.650 --> 01:00:21.090
money on the children so that
what determines how much you

01:00:21.090 --> 01:00:25.090
decide to invest in the child is
less the number of children

01:00:25.090 --> 01:00:28.080
you have total but what you
think the returns to this

01:00:28.080 --> 01:00:30.550
investment is going to be.

01:00:30.550 --> 01:00:34.470
And another thing is that in a
lot of cases the investment

01:00:34.470 --> 01:00:38.070
