01:00:55.710 --> 01:00:58.280
fixed budget constraint for
how much you can afford to

01:00:58.280 --> 01:00:59.500
spend on your children.

01:00:59.500 --> 01:01:02.070
But it's a whole family
constraint.

01:01:02.070 --> 01:01:07.010
And what is determined in
children investment is less

01:01:07.010 --> 01:01:09.950
how much money do you have or
how much time do you have, but

01:01:09.950 --> 01:01:12.260
how you decide to allocate this
budget, which corresponds

01:01:12.260 --> 01:01:16.580
more to the perception of cost
and benefits as we've seen in

01:01:16.580 --> 01:01:19.580
